{"tid":872292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"認真2000睇下玩幾耐！輸晒唔賭 再賭斬手！","createTime":"2018-10-22T14:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:10:45.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b17e7b078d6f9f8b5834a048eb1ebc9371496cd8","tid":872292,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"出名黑仔 買無入球就補時入球 買角大就差一角 買主就客勝 買半細就半大 總之買乜輸乜<br />\n<br />\n今次睇下頂唔頂到一個禮拜 上兩次都輸all in 今次認真玩 唔會再柒<br />\n<br />\n想贏錢可以試下買我對家 贏咗嘅俾張飛嚟睇下 特我戒賭戒得安心啲 死都死得眼閉<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 今晚買咗兩張！<br />\n7穿21諗住玩下 未試過穿咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d978092a1f8b854c365882e59f8cd7ad570de6","tid":872292,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"兩條飛輸晒了"},{"pid":"ae0e695525cadd4b6037adae71f71e744c0cad90","tid":872292,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66d978092a1f8b854c365882e59f8cd7ad570de6","tid":872292,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"兩條飛輸晒了"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"你咪試下買對家 贏錢記住貼飛 等大家賀下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136ce50445e30e2b4b4749f0d364220fc72eb3f0","tid":872292,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"買得幾舊水咁淆就唔洗入2000蚊啦"},{"pid":"9a2793f41b8d64e3a36bd258d02669d4ba4a9fb2","tid":872292,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0e695525cadd4b6037adae71f71e744c0cad90","tid":872292,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66d978092a1f8b854c365882e59f8cd7ad570de6","tid":872292,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"兩條飛輸晒了"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-